###
### Luma adaptive grain generating filter. Y/YUV only.
###
### FilmGrain is based on DidÃ©e's GrainFactory3 script
###
###
### +-------------+
### |  CHANGELOG  |
### +-------------+
###
### 2023.03.03
###      - Fix filter name
###      - Promote to AVS+ v3.7.3
